        "created_at": "2023-09-13T01:21:12.695Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/note.asp?iWine=89367&amp;iNote=10679768\"><b>1994 Bonneau du Martray Corton-Charlemagne</b></a> - France, Burgundy, C\u00f4te de Beaune, Corton-Charlemagne Grand Cru (9/11/2023)<br>\nRe-corked in 2022 and in very good form. Some white mushroom development along with pure white peach and lavender aromas. It is gently tropical. The palate is rich and layered and cut by Corton's steely line. Each sip unveils something else interesting and length is excellent. Wonderful aged white Burg.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Posted from <a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/\">CellarTracker</a></p>",
